                  <additions>
                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus target="#84rb">f. 84rb</locus>
                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#84rb">84rb</locus>: ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ግንዘት፡ ዘቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ደንደራ፡
                              ዘወሀቦ፡ ጌታው፡ አቶ፡ ኃይለ፡ ሥላሴ፡ ይኩኖ፡ መርሐ፡ ለመንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡…</quote>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           <note> The note states that getaw ato Ḫāyla Śǝllāse donated the book to
                              Qǝddus Mikāʾel Dändära. It also contains a supplication for Ḫāyla
                              Śǝllāse, his wife Ṣǝllatä Muse and his children. </note>
                        </item>
